summary: The document is a table of unreported cases from the Supreme Court of Ghana for the year 2005, listing various civil and chieftaincy appeals heard between January and December 2005. It includes case titles, appeal or motion numbers, and hearing dates. The cases involve diverse matters such as property disputes, human rights, administrative justice, estate issues, and chieftaincy conflicts. No detailed judgments or rulings are provided in this index-style document, which serves as a reference list rather than a full legal report.
